04:17.391 --> 04:19.391
Cheap canadian bull crap.

04:19.393 --> 04:21.059
Yeah, I'm sick of canada.

04:21.061 --> 04:23.395
Their president's
just crap trash, though.

04:23.397 --> 04:25.263
One-hit wonder.

04:25.265 --> 04:27.800
He talks too much
and not enough action.

04:27.802 --> 04:28.867
Oh, thank you, dear.

04:28.869 --> 04:32.805
Dad, if you win,
will you buy me a bird?

04:32.807 --> 04:34.339
Yeah, sure.

04:34.341 --> 04:36.208
I hope your dad
can walk to the bird store

04:36.210 --> 04:37.609
Because he ain't driving.

04:37.611 --> 04:38.543
[ laughter ]

04:38.545 --> 04:40.679
Chelsea,
go get me a coffee cake.

04:40.681 --> 04:42.681
